Use Arrow Keys To Control The Stone.
The Objective Is To Hit The Wall With The Stone.
Each Brick In The Wall Can Be Hit Multiple Times.
Be Careful Not To Loose The Stone!

The Project Uses DirectX For Rendering And BulletPhysics For All Physics Environment Setup And Control.

System Requirements:
1366×768 Resolution Supported Monitor(Recommended)
DirectX 9.0c Supported Graphics Card

Compiling Notes: DirectX SDK And Bulletphysics Must be Installed And Setup Properly In Visual Studio Before Compiling 